    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a source of quality parts? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it shows significant wear, has known mechanical issues, and will need real attention before it's road-ready at its best. That said, it's a great opportunity for a hands-on DIYer or someone who knows their way around a garage. Priced to reflect its current state, so you know exactly what you're getting \u2014 no surprises! Come take a look and see the potential for yourself. \ud83d\udd27",
