    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Flawless Mint-Condition Stunner \u2013 Like Stepping Into a Brand New Car! \ud83d\ude97\n\nIf you've been searching for a used car that genuinely feels brand new, your search ends here! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 the paint gleams, the interior is spotless, and everything runs with the smooth precision you'd expect from a showroom model. It has been impeccably maintained, and it shows in every detail. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road on weekends, this car is ready to deliver a premium driving experience from day one. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in mint condition. The exterior shows no dents, scratches, or paint damage, with a clean and uniform finish across all panels. The interior has no meaningful wear \u2014 upholstery, surfaces, and controls are all in excellent shape. Mechanically, the car functions as expected with no known issues.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, and it truly represents the finest example of a used vehicle you are likely to encounter on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or dents, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is equally impressive, showing no meaningful wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or trim pieces; everything looks and feels as close to new as a used car can get. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power, with all mechanical systems functioning exactly as intended. All electronics, including climate control, infotainment, windows, and lighting, operate without issue. This is a turn-key vehicle requiring no immediate investment \u2014 simply drive it and enjoy. Buyers who demand the very best in a pre-owned vehicle will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable Daily Driver! Looking for a practical car that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great choice for everyday commuting and getting things done. It does show some signs of normal wear and may benefit from a little TLC down the road, but it's ready to serve you well right now. A smart, budget-conscious choice for anyone who needs dependable transportation without the premium price tag!",
      "price": 16000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a full and transparent picture before you commit. The exterior shows clear signs of use \u2014 you'll notice visible scratches, some paint fading or scuffing in multiple areas, and possibly minor dents or dings from everyday driving. It's not a showroom car, but the body is structurally sound. Inside, the cabin reflects similar wear: expect faded or worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and controls that work but may show their age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 think of it as a vehicle that needs a bit of TLC rather than a turnkey daily driver in perfect shape. There may be minor mechanical quirks or maintenance items that a new owner should budget for. This is an honest, budget-friendly option for a buyer who's comfortable with a project or simply needs reliable transportation without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns to report. The interior is clean and functional, showing modest signs of everyday use such as light wear on the seat fabric and minor scuffs on trim pieces, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without issue, and all major systems are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and brakes are in serviceable condition. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been honestly maintained and is ready for its next owner. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
